{{Europe-myth-stub}}

'''L. Boyer''' was a [[France|French]] [[cyclist]]. He competed at the [[1900 Summer Olympics]] in the [[Cycling at the 1900 Summer Olympics – Men's sprint|men's sprint]]. He did not finish in the [[Cycling at the 1900 Summer Olympics – Men's sprint#Heat 3|third heat of the first round]].<ref name="SR">{{cite web | url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/bo/l-boyer-1.html | title=L. Boyer Bio, Stats and Results | publisher=sports-reference | accessdate=22 May 2016}}</ref>
