.people.com.cn/GB/channel335/336/822/200105/10/60321.html 上海宝山出土完好明代古尸]</ref> |- | [[Hazel Farris]] || USA || {{dts|1906|format=hide}} ca 1880–20 December 1906 || || |- | [[James Hepburn, 4th Earl of Bothwell]] || England || {{dts|1578|format=hide}} c. 1534–14 April 1578 || || |- | [[Ho Chi Minh]] || Vietnam || {{dts|1969|format=hide}} 19 May 1890–2 September 1969 || || |- | Huang Zhuowu (黃拙吾) || China || {{dts|1722|format=hide}} died c. [[Kangxi Emperor|Kangxi era]] || ||<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.chinareviewnews.com/doc/1011/6/2/1/101162129.html?coluid=6&kindid=29&docid=101162129 |title=專家復原"龍袍乾屍"真容 破解歷史謎案 |publisher=Chinareviewnews.com |date=9 December 2009 |accessdate=4 December 2011}}</ref> |- | [[Mummy Juanita]] || Peru || {{dts|1480|format=hide}} died c. 1450–1480 || || |- | [[Pazyryk Ice Maiden|The Ice Maiden]] || Siberia || {{dts|-500|format=hide}} 5th century BCE || [[File:Mummy of the Ukok Princess.jpg|90px]] ||<ref name="nova">{{cite web|url=https://www.pbs.org/wgbh/nova/transcripts/2517siberian.html|title=Ice Mummies: Siberian Ice Maiden|publisher=PBS – NOVA|accessdate=31 July 2007}}</ref> |- | [[Dashi-Dorzho Itigilov]] || Siberia || {{dts|1927|format=hide}} 1852–1927 || || |- | [[Christian Friedrich von Kahlbutz]] || Prussia || {{dts|1702|format=hide}} 1651–1702 || [[File:Kalebuz.jpg|90px]] || |- | [[Sogen Kato]] || Japan || {{dts|1978|format=hide}} 22 July 1899–c. November 1978 || || |- | [[Kherima Mumie]] || Brazil || {{dts|1824|format=hide}} 1804–1824 || || {{Citation needed|date=March 2016}} |- | [[Klement Gottwald]], buried || Czechoslovakia || {{dts|1953|format=hide}} 1896–1953 || || |- | [[Kim Il-Sung]] || North Korea || {{dts|1994|format=hide}} 15 April 1912–8 July 1994 || || |- | [[Kim Jong-il]] || North Korea || {{dts|2011|format=hide}} 16 February 1941–17 December 2011 || || |- | [[Vissarion Korkoliacos]] || Greece || {{dts|1991|format=hide}} 1908–1991 || || |- | [[Kwäday Dän Ts’ìnchi]] || Canada || {{dts|1700|format=hide}} born c. 1450–